Sure, here are several example sentences in Serbian that use the word "torba" in different forms and positions, with translations in English:

1. **Torbu** sam ostavio u kancelariji. (*I left the bag in the office.*)
2. Vozim se autobusom sa teškom **torbom**. (*I am riding the bus with a heavy bag.*)
3. Ona nosi mnogo stvari u svojoj **torbi**. (*She carries a lot of things in her bag.*)
4. Pitam se da li je ta **torba** dovoljno velika za moje stvari. (*I wonder if that bag is big enough for my things.*)
5. Pogledajte ovu lepu **torbu** koju sam kupila. (*Look at this beautiful bag I bought.*)
6. **Torbe** su raspoređene po čitavoj sobi. (*Bags are scattered throughout the entire room.*)
7. U prodavnici ima mnogo različitih vrsta **torbi**. (*There are many different types of bags in the store.*)
8. Moj sin je izgubio svoju omiljenu **torbu** na igralištu. (*My son lost his favorite bag at the playground.*)
9. U ovoj **torbi** držim svoje knjige. (*I keep my books in this bag.*)
10. **Torbu** bi trebalo da ostaviš u garderobi. (*You should leave your bag in the cloakroom.*)

I hope these examples help! Let me know if you have any further questions.